{"tid":106494,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣-唇上之歌","createTime":"2017-02-03T16:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T17:19:19.000Z","uid":6464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44e8c686a9724973f87f7a3ccc45ea3963d73633","tid":106494,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"我真係一個好少睇日本戲劇嘅人，不過呢套野真係幾好睇。<br />\n好睇在啲人同境實在太靚太清新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，新垣結衣真係好靚好靚，同個長崎五島都好靚好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n最令人舒服係套戲啲鏡頭拍得好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，加上filter嘅色系好靚，成套野都好pure and true。<br />\n成套戲劇情都好日式青春片，日本啲劇好多都係咁慘情咁悲劇，但悲劇得嚟永遠最後都好勵志咁有個開心嘅結局。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者呢啲就係日本人，永遠都好似有啲野屈住喺個心入面咁好忍得，但係佢地真係有種青春，有種熱血。年少輕狂唔緊要，最緊要係相信同面對自己，活在當下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫失勇氣，唇上留歌，心存太陽。<br />\n真係好鐘意呢句野，好有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇緊逃恥，好好睇好搞笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b5aa42a1216ee6d1c35d55a1b8dd4488f42119","tid":106494,"uid":16263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:51:57.000Z","msg":"結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f548c40c8acd5aefe4f9fbfeaa76bae8c01303b","tid":106494,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套係咪好冷門"},{"pid":"eeeb47dd0ca64c0518d5c006b740458c050b4465","tid":106494,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"Keep on believing"},{"pid":"2dcc1a1250f648793b5c20af8556568c56435fce","tid":106494,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"導演係青春片大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bad19b3c1850b5fa67d4a7e0a372113f0fdbb90","tid":106494,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>導演係青春片大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套啲小朋友主角<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249461956e6da34